ue_metrics_metadata.name: amf_ue_id
ue_metrics_metadata.description: AMF UE id. It is present when the UEassociated logical NG-connection is setup.

ue_metrics_metadata.name: dl_bitrate
ue_metrics_metadata.description: Downlink bitrate in bits per seconds at PHY layer level (Counts acknowledged transmissions).

ue_metrics_metadata.name: ul_bitrate
ue_metrics_metadata.description: Ul_bitrate bitrate in bits per seconds at PHY layer level (Counts acknowledged transmissions).

ue_metrics_metadata.name: dl_tx
ue_metrics_metadata.description: Number of downlink transmitted transport blocks (without retransmissions).

ue_metrics_metadata.name: ul_tx
ue_metrics_metadata.description: Number of received uplink transport blocks (withoutCRC error).

ue_metrics_metadata.name: dl_err
ue_metrics_metadata.description: Number of downlink non transmitted transport blocks (after retransmissions).

ue_metrics_metadata.name: ul_path_loss
ue_metrics_metadata.description: Last computed UL path loss in dB, estimated from PHR.
